OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779700298
OL,3,C'Suspected human remains' found in
OL,4,Cwooded area
OL,6,FAn investigation is underway after
OL,7,F'suspected human remains' were found
OL,8,Fnear Mansfield.
OL,10,FThe remains were discovered by members
OL,11,Fof the public around 2.45pm on
OL,12,FSaturday 23 May in a wooded area next
OL,13,Fto the A617 Rainworth Bypass.
OL,15,FA police cordon has been set up and is
OL,16,Fexpected to remain in place for some
OL,17,Ftime while investigations continue.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779700298
OL,3,C'Suspected human remains' found in
OL,4,Cwooded area
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Matt Scott, of
OL,7,FNottinghamshire Police, said: "I
OL,8,Funderstand a report of this nature
OL,9,Fwill likely cause concern among the
OL,10,Fcommunity; however, I would like to
OL,11,Foffer my reassurance this incident
OL,12,Fposes no risk to public safety.
OL,14,F"While the investigation is still in
OL,15,Fits early stages, following inquiries
OL,16,Fcarried out so far, I can confirm that
OL,17,Fthe remains we have found are believed
OL,18,Fto be of one person.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779700298
OL,3,C'Suspected human remains' found in
OL,4,Cwooded area
OL,6,F"The identity of this person is yet to
OL,7,Fbe established but a dedicated team of
OL,8,Fofficers are working to confirm this
OL,9,Fas soon as possible.
OL,11,F"We have a dedicated team of
OL,12,Fspecialist forensic officers carrying
OL,13,Fout lines of inquiry. This will help
OL,14,Fus better understand the circumstances
OL,15,Fof how the body came to be there and
OL,16,Fsee if there is more information about
OL,17,Fthe death which can be gathered."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779700298
OL,3,C'Suspected human remains' found in
OL,4,Cwooded area
OL,6,FDI Scott added: "Any discovery of
OL,7,Fhuman remains is taken extremely
OL,8,Fseriously. A thorough investigation is
OL,9,Fbeing carried out and we are keeping
OL,10,Fan open mind at this time.
OL,12,F"It is important for me to stress that
OL,13,Fthis is also likely to take us some
OL,14,Ftime yet. There will still be a scene
OL,15,Fremaining that will be guarded by
OL,16,Fpolice officers for a number of days
OL,17,Fwhile our work continues.
OL,26,@nD@QOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,363,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F362A1779700298
OL,3,C'Suspected human remains' found in
OL,4,Cwooded area
OL,6,F"As our investigation progresses over
OL,7,Fthe Bank Holiday weekend and into next
OL,8,Fweek, residents can expect to see an
OL,9,Fincreased police presence in the area.
OL,10,FI would encourage anyone with any
OL,11,Fconcerns to please come and speak to
OL,12,Fus.
OL,14,F"We would like to thank the public for
OL,15,Ftheir patience. We know the effect
OL,16,Fthis investigation will have had on
OL,17,Fresidents living in the area.
OL,19,F"As always, we will keep people
OL,20,Fupdated as this complex investigation
OL,21,Fdevelops."
OL,26,@vD@AOU{D@AOU}D@JO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
